472
00:36:52,713 --> 00:36:55,191
O que houve?

473
00:37:03,211 --> 00:37:05,339
Boa noite, mãe.

474
00:37:11,060 --> 00:37:13,356
Boa noite, querida.

475
00:37:16,928 --> 00:37:18,671
Boa noite.

476
00:37:33,758 --> 00:37:36,821
Não me machuque, querida.

